character.name: Create a realistic male character in his early-to-mid 20s with a serious, calm expression. He has a medium-light to olive skin tone and a symmetrical face with sharp, well-defined features. His eyebrows are thick, dark, and slightly straight with a natural arch. His eyes are dark brown, almond-shaped, and slightly hooded, conveying a focused, introspective gaze. He has a straight, proportionate nose and full lips with a defined cupid’s bow. His facial hair includes a neatly trimmed short beard and mustache that evenly frame the jawline and chin.  His hair is dark brown to black, short and slightly tousled with a natural texture and a subtle fringe at the front. He wears small stud earrings in both ears.  Dress him in a black hooded sweatshirt layered under a black padded jacket with a matte finish, giving off a clean, modern urban streetwear aesthetic. The jacket should appear slightly bulky and structured. Pair this with black baggy jeans featuring a relaxed fit, and black Jordan sneakers to complete the contemporary street-style look.  His posture is relaxed with shoulders slightly forward. The overall mood should be minimal, moody, and highly realistic, featuring soft indoor lighting and a neutral background.
